#

Lemon Zest Waffles

30 min
$5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

GlutenDairyEggs

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

BreakfastBrunchEasy

Description

Light and fluffy waffles infused with refreshing lemon zest, perfect for a delightful breakfast or brunch!

Ingredients

  • all-purpose flour: 2 cups
  • baking powder: 2 tablespoons
  • sugar: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: 1/2 teaspoon
  • eggs: 2
  • milk: 1 3/4 cups
  • unsalted butter: 1/2 cup
  • lemon zest: 2 tablespoons
  • vanilla extract: 1 teaspoon
